cards.cardContent: You open all the lockers but find nothing, except for the last one that is closed. Maybe you can find the key somewhere in the room... (You can combine this card with another one by adding their number and searching the corresponding card)
You find some keys inside the bin! Maybe they can open something in the room! (To combine object try to add their number and look for the corresponding card if it exists)
Congrats, you've opened the locker! Inside, you find SOMETHING.
Despite the ping pong pad that shows how cool this company is, you can see some stools of various colors hanged into the wall.
